WORK SUMMARY :
Task was given on converting the react.js app to SPA using React routing.  Implemented routing functionality to navigate between different pages such as Home, About
and Contact without reloading the page. Used React Router components like Browser Router, Routes, and Route to define and manage application routes. 
Designed a navigation bar with links to allow users to switch between pages smoothly within the application.

LEARNING OUTCOMES :
·  Learned the concept of Single Page Applications (SPA) and how routing works in React.
·  Gained practical knowledge of React Router for handling navigation between multiple components/pages.
